data.description: Come check out this adorable 3-bedroom, 1.5-bathroom home in Hurst Terrace Addition. Recently repainted with vinyl flooring, and fairly new carpet in the bedrooms, this charming residence boasts an updated bathroom, a gas cooktop, and an oven. Relax by the wood-burning fireplace on cozy evenings. The HVAC system is relatively new (5-6 years old), and a nice size utility room. The spacious backyard offers a shed and covered patio. A park within walking distance,  and it's conveniently located for easy access to both Dallas and Fort Worth.
